text: thumb Neu-Baumburg Castle (, also Neu-Bamberg, Neuenbaumburg, Novobeimburg and Neubamberg) is a ruined castle in the town of Neu-Bamberg in Rhineland- Palatinate, Germany. ==Notes and references== ==Sources and external links== *www.burgeninventar.de in German only.
